episode_summary: In this episode, Jeff Biebuyck shares his journey from the entertainment industry to becoming a top real estate agent specializing in luxury properties. He discusses the importance of leveraging technology and AI to future-proof your business, the value of learning from failures, and building strong referral networks. Jeff also provides insights into current market challenges and the strategies he's using to adapt and thrive.
